OL,3,CJohn Lewis reveals job interview
OL,4,Cquestions online as part of
OL,5,Cinclusivity drive
OL,7,Fhas started publishing interview
OL,8,Fquestions online, in a move which
OL,9,Fcould benefit neurodiverse applicants.
OL,11,FPeople applying for jobs at the retail
OL,12,Fgroup, which also includes Waitrose,
OL,13,Fcan now view a list of compliancy-
OL,14,Fbased interview questions
OL,16,FThe move is designed so applicants can
OL,17,Ftake the time to think about their
OL,18,Fpast experiences and skills, and
OL,19,Fprepare different examples to take to
OL,20,Finterview.
