OL,3,CJohn Lewis reveals job interview
OL,4,Cquestions online as part of
OL,5,Cinclusivity drive
OL,7,FIt is expected to help the retailer
OL,8,Fattract people from a variety of
OL,9,Fbackgrounds, and to have specific
OL,10,Fbenefits for neurodiverse people,
OL,11,Fwhich can include autistic people, or
OL,12,Fthose with ADHD or dyslexia.
OL,14,FThe group stressed that interviews
OL,15,Fwill still be in-depth with detailed
OL,16,Ffollow-up questions, and that people
OL,17,Fwill not know which specific questions
OL,18,Fwill be used during their interview.
