OL,3,CJohn Lewis reveals job interview
OL,4,Cquestions online as part of
OL,5,Cinclusivity drive
OL,7,F"Interviews can feel daunting, and for
OL,8,Fsome - particularly those who are
OL,9,Fneurodiverse - nerves can seriously
OL,10,Fimpact performance," said Lorna
OL,11,FBullett, the head of talent
OL,12,Facquisition for John Lewis Partnership
OL,13,F(JLP).
OL,15,F"Anyone who has ever recruited will
OL,16,Fknow that there are sometimes
OL,17,Fcandidates who would be capable of
OL,18,Fperforming to a high standard in a
OL,19,Frole but don't always give the best
OL,20,Fperformance at an interview.
