OL,7,F"It made us question why we couldn't
OL,8,Fdo something different with the
OL,9,Fassessment process and we decided to
OL,10,Fpublish our interview questions."
OL,12,FShe said there had been early signs
OL,13,Fthe move was working well for the
OL,14,Fcompany and its candidates.
OL,16,FThe National Autistic Society
OL,17,Frecommends that employers provide
OL,18,Fquestions a few days in advance for
OL,19,Fautistic people who can have more
OL,20,Fdifficulty processing information
OL,21,Fquickly.
