OL,7,FHe said: "Providing questions in
OL,8,Fadvance is one important adjustment
OL,9,Fthat employers can do to the interview
OL,10,Fprocess to make employment more
OL,11,Faccessible to all, particularly
OL,12,Fautistic people who can face huge
OL,13,Fbarriers in finding and staying in
OL,14,Fwork.
OL,16,F"Autistic people have a huge amount to
OL,17,Foffer employers, and more and more
OL,18,Fbusinesses are recognising the
OL,19,Fbenefits of having a diverse workforce
OL,20,Ffull of people who offer a variety of
OL,21,Fskills and different ways of thinking.
