OL,7,F"It is vital that employers are open
OL,8,Fto reasonable adjustments."
OL,10,FJLP's initiative goes further than
OL,11,Fmaking "reasonable adjustments" to the
OL,12,Frecruitment process for disabled
OL,13,Fpeople, which is a legal requirement
OL,14,Ffor UK companies.
