OL,7,FInterview questions published by JLP
OL,8,Finclude "tell me about a time when you
OL,9,Factively stepped in to improve
OL,10,Fteamwork and collaboration within a
OL,11,Fteam", and "when have you taken the
OL,12,Ftime to provide very difficult
OL,13,Ffeedback to someone?"
OL,15,FTom Cornell, a psychology consultant
OL,16,Fat HireVue, said employers should be
OL,17,Fencouraged to rethink their hiring
OL,18,Fprocesses to embrace neurodiversity.
