OL,7,FHe said: "When organisations seek to
OL,8,Fenhance neurodiversity within their
OL,9,Fworkforce, a crucial starting point is
OL,10,Fevaluating their recruitment processes.
OL,12,F"Frequently, traditional hiring
OL,13,Fmethods, such as lengthy cover letters
OL,14,Fand face-to-face interviews, directly
OL,15,Fput neurodiverse candidates at a
OL,16,Fdisadvantage.
